laboratory_examinations.findings: Initially revealed hematocolpos; after two-and-half months, showed hematometra and hematocolpos.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Changed from hematocolpos to hematometra and hematocolpos.

laboratory_examinations.findings: Initially revealed a thick transverse vaginal septum in the upper one-third of the vagina; repeat MRI revealed a 3 to 4 centimeter thick septum with stenosed vagina.
laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Increased thickness of the septum from initially thick to 3 to 4 centimeters.
